  "is_bundle": false,
  "feature_bullets": [
    "【Filters 99.9% Chlorine】 Transform your bath time with our easy-to-use bath filter. This convenient bathroom accessory enhances your relaxation and well-being by reducing chlorine levels up to 99.9%, ensuring a pure, soothing bath.This bath faucet water filter will leave your skin and hair feeling refreshed and nourished.",
    "【Adds Essential Minerals】Infuse your bath with essential minerals like magnesium and zinc to promote softer skin and smoother hair. This water filter helps retain your skin’s natural moisture, making it ideal for sensitive skin, babies, and young children. Santevia’s Bath Filter naturally combats diaper rash, eczema or dry and itchy skin.",
    "【Anti-Slip Design】The newly designed anti-slip silicone strap ensures that the Santevia Bath Filter is compatible with most bathtub faucet filters, providing a secure and stable fit.",
    "【Easy Installation】Our easy-to-install bathtub faucet filter is designed for effortless use. Simply attach it to your bathtub faucet, and enjoy the benefits of filtered water without the hassle of complicated setups. It's the perfect addition to your bathroom accessories collection!",
    "【Care Instructions】After each use, rinse the Santevia Bath Filter thoroughly and allow it to air dry completely before the next use. For best results, avoid leaving the filter on the bath faucet or in a humid environment. The Santevia Bath Filter offers a lifespan of 2 months or 4,755 gal that outlasts many competitors on the market."
  ],
  "feature_bullets_count": 5,
  "feature_bullets_flat": "【Care Instructions】After each use, rinse the Santevia Bath Filter thoroughly and allow it to air dry completely before the next use. For best results, avoid leaving the filter on the bath faucet or in a humid environment. The Santevia Bath Filter offers a lifespan of 2 months or 4,755 gal that outlasts many competitors on the market. 【Easy Installation】Our easy-to-install bathtub faucet filter is designed for effortless use. Simply attach it to your bathtub faucet, and enjoy the benefits of filtered water without the hassle of complicated setups. It's the perfect addition to your bathroom accessories collection!. 【Anti-Slip Design】The newly designed anti-slip silicone strap ensures that the Santevia Bath Filter is compatible with most bathtub faucet filters, providing a secure and stable fit. 【Adds Essential Minerals】Infuse your bath with essential minerals like magnesium and zinc to promote softer skin and smoother hair. This water filter helps retain your skin’s natural moisture, making it ideal for sensitive skin, babies, and young children. Santevia’s Bath Filter naturally combats diaper rash, eczema or dry and itchy skin. 【Filters 99.9% Chlorine】 Transform your bath time with our easy-to-use bath filter. This convenient bathroom accessory enhances your relaxation and well-being by reducing chlorine levels up to 99.9%, ensuring a pure, soothing bath.This bath faucet water filter will leave your skin and hair feeling refreshed and nourished.",
