      "id": "RDWDGLB7CJ6AA",
      "title": "Takes contaminants out of water and is affordable.",
      "body": "Best bath filter for your tub, easily stays on your faucet with the Velcro straps. Water flows nicely through filter without pouring over the top and takes 100% of the chlorine smell out of my bathwater. Peace of mind for my children, not absorbing harmful chemicals and really affordable.",
